    CUSTOM RESPONSIVE CAR SHOP UI (ROBLOX LUA)
    Features:
    - Draggable Window (Modern smooth dragging)
    - Resizable Window (Scale-invariant, interactive handle on bottom-right)
    - Auto-adjusting Grid Layout (Resizes cleanly alongside the window)
    - Dynamic Page Scanning (Handles "Page1", "page11", and "ppage20" naming anomalies)
    - Clean Modern Design (Dark Mode theme with rounded corners and drop-shadow styling)
    - Interactive Spawning: Automatically despawns current vehicle and spawns selected one
--]]

